title: Ocelot Sport Quad ATV/UTV Tire All Terrain Bounty Hunter of fun 18x9.5-8 P311
description: The Ocelot P311 tires are comparable to the Kenda Bounty Hunter ST tires. These tires feature large, rugged lugs that stand up to wear and tear and are well spaced to allow for mud, rocks, and other debris to sling out while rolling. With thick shoulder lugs that provide additional traction, these tires are good for trudging through deep ruts. Overlapping center tread helps deliver a smoother and quieter ride.
